product_name: Keen Brooklyn II Canvas Travel Bag - Women's
long_description: Carry all you need for the day in the women's Keen Brooklyn II Canvas Travel Bag, whether you're commuting downtown or leaving town altogether for the weekend. Made of soft linen/cotton canvas with a ticking-stripe lining. Roomy interior holds a lot of gear, such as a water bottle, umbrella and lunch. Rear exterior pocket is great for magazines, boarding passes or a paperback. Adjustable shoulder strap has recycled-aluminum components. Keen Brooklyn II Canvas Travel Bag has a front organizer and drop-in pockets.
